{"tid":1721890,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以去日本攞d 分解二噁英嘅菌返香港養？","createTime":"2019-11-14T19:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T15:31:50.000Z","uid":79974,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1aece8272b25d45f71412d6f8575d24e7b815cfd","tid":1721890,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:19:11.000Z","msg":"在2006年1月16日出版的《自然生物科技雜誌》，京都大學的微生物學教授村田幸作發表論文，指他們的研究利用基因技術，把兩種不同品種的鞘脂單胞菌屬的基因混合而培育出來的超級細菌，能夠吞噬戴奧辛類化合物（即二噁英），並以前所未有的短時間將之在其體內分解。<br />\n<br />\nby wiki<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/二噁英\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E4%BA%8C%E5%99%81%E8%8B%B1&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc61gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=2978ca63\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/二噁英</a>"},{"pid":"25028c82fed931e874dc67a1f7edbad4c97f75b3","tid":1721890,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:19:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"302cde0fac261673fdea0d9c6fc67370ff6864ce","tid":1721890,"uid":79974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"dca2c2e3fcce10be846e4aa42f0cc6cc8f9641ca","tid":1721890,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:19:52.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"194c5324364ce945e49432eaeb1adf5f2d7a0b1a","tid":1721890,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:20:04.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"94c4041ecdb5f86e1956266e1a8f5f5c935dab9e","tid":1721890,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:20:14.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"e0057c31688f981816e7e88522043c5f709bc057","tid":1721890,"uid":249026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f692e0ece4d6ebc981e09c8c04c7c73aa4f66994","tid":1721890,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,